response.overview: Maya Mall is a Telugu movie starring Dilip Kumar and Eesha Rebba in prominent roles. The cast also includes Diksha Panth and Thagubothu Ramesh. It is a thriller suspense movie directed by Govindh Lalam, with K.V Hari Krishna as the producer, Sai Karthik as the music director, forming part of the crew.
response.title: Maya Mall
